{"tid":1096170,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"喺lounge 食碗魚蛋粉","createTime":"2019-04-07T14:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T14:18:30.000Z","uid":61697,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4759570c9fec3c6db8e85d399734fd3e8723e6a1","tid":1096170,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"夜晚落機 餓餓地就去食碗魚蛋粉<br />\n排前面喺一位40歲左右嘅男士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 魚蛋粉姐姐<br />\n<br />\n姐姐裝好碗魚蛋粉<br />\n<br />\n男士：Any vegetable?<br />\n姐姐（黑人問號）：吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男士（強調）：Vegetable.<br />\n姐姐：？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男士：That's ok. <br />\n咁就拎碗魚蛋粉返位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知我坐低 就聽到個位地中海頭既男士 用超純正廣東話同佢爸爸媽媽傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實咁喺咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebd531f367df9e2f6c7012688cf2fc388388f18","tid":1096170,"uid":139526,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"巴閉囉 疊馬囉 英雄主義"},{"pid":"5fa1b87b623f69b58dd22e2495f98293f02032d6","tid":1096170,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4512c93c7db91a6d8a7cd027c7454bc84ea3833c","tid":1096170,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"Okay,  its funny"},{"pid":"0c622920a35014a3c48f44b1cc7b6ef392da2eff","tid":1096170,"uid":93350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:15:29